io.advantageous.qbit.service

Class Protocol

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.advantageous.qbit.service.Protocol

  • public class Protocol
extends java.lang.Object
    Protocol constants for QBit Websocket/HTTP support. This defines constants for HTTP request params as well as constants for parsing a websocket stream.

    Created by Richard on 9/26/14.
